      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GUMTREE HILL (6) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only 1.3 lengths from King Litterbug in third (19.61) at this track. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Can go on with it. KING CHERRY (8) rocketed out of the inside draw with a strong early sectional and gave a sight but had to settle for a placing, finishing second (19.58) at this track over 350m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expecting another good run. BARKING BLUE (7) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and three placings from nine starts. Missed the frame latest (29.57) when fourth over 510m at Sale in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. Suited here and expected to run well. ZIPPI MUSTANG (3) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
